title: Yahoo Lifestyle
text: You are a bright ray of sunshine in someones overcast sky. Hanging out with a friend likely cheers them up considerably today, even if they dont let on that anythings wrong. The buoyant Leo Moon shines in your 11th House of Friendship, so you both benefit from doing something fun thats energizing and entertaining, like going to a comedy club or watching an inspirational movie. Perhaps you discover that empowering others boosts your spirits, too. Positivity, like love, boomerangs back to you when you let it fly free. Get Your Complete Cosmic Profile
